Here is the equivalent COBOL code:

```
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FILE-SKILL.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  FILE-PATH     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
01  CONTENT       PIC X(2000) VALUE SPACES.
01  MESSAGE       PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
01  SB            PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.

SCREEN SECTION.
01  FILL-IN.   FROM FS TO FS
    LINE 1 COL 1 TO 20
    VALUE "FILE-SKILL".

Procedure Division.
READ-FILE Procedure Using BY CONTENT
    CALL 'ReadFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    DISPLAY CONTENT
    IF CONTENT NOT = SPACES THEN
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "❌ Datei nicht gefunden: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        STRING "❌ Fehler beim Lesen: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.

WRITE-FILE Procedure Using BY CONTENT FILE-PATH
    CALL 'WriteFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    DISPLAY CONTENT
    IF CONTENT NOT = SPACES THEN
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "💾 Datei erfolgreich geschrieben: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        STRING "❌ Fehler beim Schreiben: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.

LIST-FILES Procedure Using BY CONTENT FILE-PATH
    CALL 'ListFiles' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    DISPLAY CONTENT
    IF CONTENT NOT = SPACES THEN
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "❌ Ordner nicht gefunden: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        STRING "❌ Fehler beim Auflisten: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.

DELETE-FILE Procedure Using BY CONTENT FILE-PATH
    CALL 'DeleteFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    DISPLAY CONTENT
    IF CONTENT NOT = SPACES THEN
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "🗑️ Datei erfolgreich gelöscht: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        STRING "❌ Datei existiert nicht: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.

ReadFile Function Returns(STRING)
    MOVE ZERO TO SB
    IF FILE-PATH IS NOT ALNUM THEN
        STRING "❌ Datei nicht gefunden: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        ACCEPT CONTENT FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
        RETURN MESSAGE
    END-IF.
END ReadFile.

WriteFile Function Returns(STRING)
    MOVE ZERO TO SB
    IF FILE-PATH IS NOT ALNUM THEN
        STRING "❌ Fehler beim Schreiben: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        ACCEPT CONTENT FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "💾 Datei erfolgreich geschrieben: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.
END WriteFile.

ListFiles Function Returns(STRING)
    MOVE ZERO TO SB
    IF FILE-PATH IS NOT ALNUM THEN
        STRING "❌ Ordner nicht gefunden: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "Ordner:" FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY MESSAGE INTO MESSAGE
        STRING "Dateien:" FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY MESSAGE INTO MESSAGE
        RETURN MESSAGE
    END-IF.
END ListFiles.

DeleteFile Function Returns(STRING)
    MOVE ZERO TO SB
    IF FILE-PATH IS NOT ALNUM THEN
        STRING "❌ Datei existiert nicht: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "🗑️ Datei erfolgreich gelöscht: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    END-IF.
END DeleteFile.

Procedure Main
    DISPLAY "FS"
    ACCEPT FILE-PATH FROM KEYBOARD
    CALL 'ReadFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    IF CONTENT NOT = SPACES THEN
        ACCEPT MESSAGE FROM KEYBOARD
        STRING "❌ Datei nicht gefunden: " FUNCTION REPLACING ALL SPACE BY CONTENT INTO MESSAGE
    ELSE
        CALL 'WriteFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
        CALL 'ListFiles' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
        CALL 'DeleteFile' USING BY CONTENT FILE-PATH BY CONTENT
    END-IF.
STOP RUN.

```

Please note that COBOL is a different language from C# and some concepts like async/await, try/catch blocks are not directly translatable.